/*
JavaScript submit event occurs when user clicks on submit button to submit the form. 
Submit event is generally used to ask for confirmation from user to submit the form. 
*/
Ex:-
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
   <meta charset="UTF-8">
   <title> JavaScript OnSubmit Event </title>
</head>
<body>
    <form action="../index.php" method="post" onsubmit="alert('Form data will be submitted to the server!');">
        <label>First Name:</label>
        <input type="text" name="first-name" required>
        <input type="submit" value="Submit">
    </form>
</body>
</html>  
